<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• فُتن فلانٌ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - أصابته فتنة فذهب مالُه أو عقلُه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢ - ابتُلي واختُبر وامتُحن <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{يَاقَوْمِ إِنَّمَا فُتِنْتُمْ بِهِ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٣ - عُذِّب <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{هَاجَرُوا مِنْ بَعْدِ مَا فُتِنُوا}</span> - <span class="c3">{يَوْمَ هُمْ عَلَى النَّارِ يُفْتَنُونَ}</span> "</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
